<p>Cardano&#8217;s treasury system plays a pivotal role in project funding, ensuring financial sustainability through its governance structure. The treasury system is designed to allocate funds for development, marketing, and community initiatives within the Cardano ecosystem. By distributing funds based on community voting, the treasury system promotes transparency and inclusivity in decision-making processes.</p>



