<p>One of the key aspects of incentivizing participation is through the use of metadata and catalysts. Metadata allows stakeholders to provide additional information about their proposals, enabling the community to make more informed decisions. Catalysts, on the other hand, provide financial incentives for stakeholders to contribute their ideas and expertise to the network.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Upgrading the Ecosystem: Governance Model Influence on Cardano&#8217;s Evolution</h2>



