<p>Cardano&#8217;s governance model plays a vital role in ensuring seamless protocol upgrades. It provides a structured framework for decision-making and consensus among stakeholders. This model involves three main entities: the Cardano Foundation, IOHK, and Emurgo. Together, they collaborate to propose, evaluate, and implement improvements in a transparent and decentralized manner.</p>



